d:T6b8,🚀 Your UI/UX Secret Weapon: Turning Clicks into Conversions

You have seconds to capture attention. If your UI/UX isn't intuitive, users leave. That’s where I come in.

I design high-converting, user-friendly interfaces that make navigation effortless and engagement seamless. With 6+ years of experience & $40K+ in Upwork earnings, I’ve helped businesses like Government of Dubai, Kruzee, Merch and others create digital experiences that drive results.

✅ Why Work With Me?
🔹 More Conversions, More Growth – Data-driven designs that increase engagement
🔹 Pixel-Perfect & Responsive – Consistency across web & mobile
🔹 Effortless Handoffs – Developer-friendly files for a smooth workflow
🔹 Scalable UI/UX Systems – Future-proofing your design investment

📌 Success Stories (Real Impact, Real Results)
💡 Kuwait’s Largest Bank: Redesigned their mobile banking app, improving user retention by 20% and streamlining transactions.

💡 Healthcare SaaS CRM: Designed a custom dashboard that reduced workflow bottlenecks by 40% and improved efficiency.
Review: Did great job understand the task at hand and completing it to specification. Also had great ideas when we needed some creative designs.

💡 ForkToFit (Food Delivery App): Built a sleek UI/UX that boosted user engagement by 35% within months.

🛠️ My Tools & Expertise
✔ Figma | Adobe XD | Sketch – UI/UX Wireframes, Prototypes, & Design Systems
✔ Landing Pages | SaaS Dashboards | Mobile Apps | Web UI/UX
✔ User Research & Testing – Data-backed decision-making

